<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="kr">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Noto+Sans+KR:500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="stylesheets/style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
  <title>DevEvents</title>
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <div id="header-logo-wrapper">
      <img id="logo" src="images/gsm-logo.png" alt="광주소프트웨어마이스터고등학교">
    </div>
  </header>
  <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.gstar.or.kr/">
    <section id="g-star-section">
      <img id="main-image" src="images/main-image.png" alt="main-image">
      <img id="gstar-image" src="images/gstar-image.png" alt="gstar-image">
    </section>
  </a>
  <section id="devfest-section" style="background-image: url(images/devfest.jpg);">
    <img id="devfest-title" src="images/devfest-logo.png" alt="devfest">
    <div id="event-list">
      <%_ devfestJSON.forEach(function(data) { -%>
      <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="<%= data.hyperlink %>">
        <div class="event-info" style="background-image: url(<%= data.imagelink %>); background-size: cover">
          <span class="event-title"><%= data.title %></span>
          <span class="event-date">📅 <%= data.date %></span>
          <span class="event-price"><%= data.price %></span>
          <span class="event-location">@ <%= data.location %></span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <%_ }); -%>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="others-section">
    <div id="general-title">Others</div>
    <div id="event-list">
      <%_ othersJSON.forEach(function(data) { -%>
      <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="<%= data.hyperlink %>">
        <div class="event-info" style="background-image: url(<%= data.imagelink %>); background-size: cover">
          <span class="event-title"><%= data.title %></span>
          <span class="event-date">📅 <%= data.date %></span>
          <span class="event-price"><%= data.price %></span>
          <span class="event-location">@ <%= data.location %></span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <%_ }); -%>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="footer-section">
    <div id="general-title">Coming Soon!</div>
    <div id="message">현재 전공 행사 안내 사이트가 미숙한 점 양해 부탁드립니다...😿😰 앞으로 더 풍성한 사이트가 될 때까지 여유를 가지고 기다려주세요!</div>
  </section>
</body>

</html>